ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great course. Helps open up your mind and sharpen writing skills.
Depends on interest or need of the student.....
Yes I would recommend it. It allows students to think critically about research and learn about major historical economic events.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This course broadened my knowledge about historical events which are important from an economics perspective. This course also taught me to think critically about research.
